{"title":"翻身谣","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":10,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湾腰地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小三娶个大姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在家能纺花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下地能帮忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都说小三转了运，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子过得强又强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小三摇头开言道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说什么命好运气强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不是分了八亩湾腰地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那有小三娶的大姑娘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不是来了共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小三还得拉芥桑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱是胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地是根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少钱没地难煞人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到街前没人问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑姑姨姨不认亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻得身打颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿得头发晕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然来了八路军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导咱们翻了身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刨穷根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栽富根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"减租减息救穷人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了钱，壮了胆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了地，扎上根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蒋要来打内战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不拚了是龟孙。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}